Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Database

  • public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles the printer and toner collections. Stores the objects in a hashset. Both printers and toners use a UID and one unique attribute to create the hash. Importing CSV files Saving and loading .xml files through JAXB
